## What I Worked On Today

Task S-5 requires the development of a system-level continuous monitoring strategy that addresses: the frequency of monitoring for each control category, the tools and methods used, the personnel responsible, the metrics that will be collected, the thresholds that trigger escalation, and how monitoring results feed back into the risk management process. Today I work through each of those components for OpenMRS at MyClinic.

